main event: A white, elongated object was observed moving rapidly and erratically over Kelly AFB, Texas on 8 August 1956.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 13 minutes., Only one object was reported., The object's movements resembled those of a balloon., There were multiple observations of round white objects in the same area shortly after., Previous sightings showed consistent behaviors with erratic flight patterns.
witness description: No witnesses were confirmed in the reports.
